    "Data cleaning identifies and corrects errors, inaccuracies, missing values, and duplicates in a table dataset to improve its quality and reliability for further analysis [50].",
    "This stage needs to identify erroneous parts and impute errors or missing values, utilizing techniques like cell population or column type annotation.Data CRUD includes the following tasks: table QA, table fact verification, NL2SQL, and spreadsheet manipulation.",
